          exercise: "Try your first official Deep Work Session! Step 1: Do your Deep Work Ritual. Step 2: Write down one specific goal on a sticky note and place it where you can see it. Step 3: Set a timer for 20 minutes (younger kids can try 15 minutes). Step 4: Start working and focus only on your goal. If a random thought or urge pops up, jot it on a 'later' list and keep working. Step 5: When the timer goes off, stop and check — did you meet your goal? Write down what you accomplished and how it felt. Rate your focus from 1 to 5 stars!",
